## Modifying the tree

To add a node, edit `tree.py`: append a `Node(...)` to the parent's
`children=[...]` list, and add a matching view stub in `views.py`. Re-run
`pmstate validate` to confirm.

To add a new event type, edit `pmstate.yaml` under `events:` and re-run
`pmstate init --upgrade`. This refreshes `tree.py` and appends new view
or reducer stubs without overwriting your existing edits.
